. LikeBTN now adds/ removes the postID of the post the user has un/liked to a collection called: /postData/UserID/likes
.Fixed typo error in props when clicking on username in searchbar and the data passed to this object didn't receive the userID from Search Screen which navigated the user to blank profile page.
.Created Post object which is universal for pictures and videos .Created chatBTN
.Integrated Search.js into new app design .Created New ProfileIcon_And_Username.js .Created Trending feeds basic page .Updated search screen to include profile icons and text Fixed Bug - Chat Nav Icon disappeared Shows message on feed instead of blank screen if the user isnt following anyone. .Refactoring .Likes works on Videos page
